data.text: Odisha Civil Services Exam Dates Out! This is for the Mains Exam of the 2022 cycle. The exam will be held from 25th February to 3rd March 2024. For the latest 2023 cycle, the OPSC has announced 399 vacancies for recruitment through the Odisha Civil Services Exam 2023. Interested candidates can apply online from 17th January 2024 to 16th February 2024. The OPSC conducts the Odisha Civil Services Exam to recruit candidates for various Group A and Group B posts under the Odisha Government. Candidates who have completed graduation are eligible for this exam. The selection process for OPSC OAS includes Prelims, Mains Written Exam, and Interview. The recruitment is also ongoing for Odisha Civil Services 2021, and 2022 cycles. Candidates must take the OPSC OAS mock tests to evaluate their performance. The OPSC OAS previous year papers are a great source of revision.
